    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"133339\">Mirek Olšák</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113488-general/topic/Proving.20termination.20with.20List.2EShortlex/near/548022557\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Thanks! On my computer, I had to explicitly unwrap <code>simp [WellFounded.wrap]</code>, but that might be just an old Lean version...</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>That was <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/pull/1308\">batteries#1308</a></p>",
        "id": 548023557,
        "sender_full_name": "Aaron Liu",
