        "sender_full_name": "Mirek Olšák",
        "timestamp": 1761856114
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Agreed! I am not suggesting/demanding that this should be done, I just wanted to mention that I thought of it before. This was right before I discovered <code>wrap</code> which is a good enough tool.</p>",
        "id": 548027792,
        "sender_full_name": "Malvin Gattinger",
